{"type":"message","id":"a15abfce","parentId":"f10f2c38","timestamp":"2026-03-15T23:44:41.234Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"This explains the zero scores! Most markets (5,017 out of 6,059) have a midpoint of exactly 0.5, which means they're not showing any price movement. The spreads are also very wide (0.998), indicating low liquidity or inactive markets.\n\nAccording to SOUL.md, I need to initiate the \"Cold Start\" fallback. Let me use the polymarket_tools to manually analyze markets. First, let me check what commands are available:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_WcPX44jdhmijJwRzVTkmWJHt","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.openclaw/skills/market-scarper && ls -la polymarket_tools/"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":272,"output":161,"cacheRead":24960,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":25393,"cost":{"input":7.616e-11,"output":6.762e-11,"cacheRead":6.9888e-10,"cacheWrite":0,"total":8.4266e-10}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773618274104}}
