{"type":"message","id":"7fef5966","parentId":"4f0293f1","timestamp":"2026-03-15T23:47:38.903Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Excellent! Now I have 30 actionable markets with significant price movements, volume > 100, and liquidity > 500. These fit the \"Mid-Volume Mandate\" from SOUL.md.\n\nNow I need to expand this list to 90 markets as per the pipeline requirement. Let me look for other types of anomalies:\n\n1. **Volume Shocks** - Markets with unusually high volume relative to their average\n2. **Spread Anomalies** - Markets with widening spreads\n3. **Information Drift** - Markets with consistent price movement in one direction\n4. **Ghost Awakens** - Low liquidity markets with sudden price moves\n\nLet me search for markets with high volume-to-liquidity ratios (volume shocks):"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_heIngClQbKM9wKEqjkCHrLAu","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.openclaw/skills/market-scarper && source venv/bin/activate && python3 -c \"\nimport sqlite3\nimport pandas as pd\nconn = sqlite3.connect('polymarket.db')\n\n# Get markets with high volume relative to liquidity (volume shocks)\nquery = '''\nSELECT \n    m.market_id,\n    m.question,\n    m.slug,\n    mc.last_trade_price,\n    mc.volume,\n    mc.liquidity,\n    CASE \n        WHEN mc.liquidity > 0 THEN mc.volume / mc.liquidity \n        ELSE 0 \n    END as volume_liquidity_ratio,\n    mc.datetime as last_update\nFROM markets m\nJOIN market_change mc ON m.change_id = mc.change_id\nWHERE LOWER(m.status) = 'active'\nAND mc.volume > 1000\nAND mc.liquidity > 500\nAND mc.liquidity < 10000  # Mid-volume range\nORDER BY volume_liquidity_ratio DESC\nLIMIT 30\n'''\n\ndf = pd.read_sql(query, conn)\nprint('Markets with high volume-to-liquidity ratios (Volume Shocks):')\nprint(df[['question', 'last_trade_price', 'volume', 'liquidity', 'volume_liquidity_ratio']].to_string())\nprint(f'\\\\nFound {len(df)} potential volume shock markets.')\nconn.close()\n\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":1455,"output":489,"cacheRead":47808,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":49752,"cost":{"input":4.074e-10,"output":2.0538e-10,"cacheRead":1.3386240000000001e-9,"cacheWrite":0,"total":1.951404e-9}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773618440640}}
