{"type":"message","id":"4f554119","parentId":"d8a1c39c","timestamp":"2026-03-15T23:49:07.593Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"No Ghost Awakens markets found. That's okay. Now I have:\n1. 30 markets with significant price movements (>10%)\n2. 30 markets with volume shocks\n\nI need 90 total markets. Let me get 30 more markets by looking for markets with consistent price movements (Information Drift) or other anomalies. Let me search for markets in traditionally volatile categories:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_VpmntcB8VUO14Zu3ugu3H3l3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.openclaw/skills/market-scarper && source venv/bin/activate && python3 -c \"\nimport sqlite3\nimport pandas as pd\nconn = sqlite3.connect('polymarket.db')\n\n# Get markets in volatile categories with decent volume and liquidity\nquery = '''\nSELECT \n    m.market_id,\n    m.question,\n    m.slug,\n    mc.last_trade_price,\n    mc.volume,\n    mc.liquidity,\n    m.market_category,\n    mc.datetime as last_update\nFROM markets m\nJOIN market_change mc ON m.change_id = mc.change_id\nWHERE LOWER(m.status) = 'active'\nAND mc.volume > 500\nAND mc.liquidity > 1000\nAND mc.liquidity < 50000\nAND (\n    m.market_category LIKE '%Politics%' OR\n    m.market_category LIKE '%Crypto%' OR\n    m.market_category LIKE '%Sports%' OR\n    m.market_category LIKE '%Election%' OR\n    m.market_category LIKE '%Trump%' OR\n    m.market_category LIKE '%Ukraine%'\n)\nORDER BY mc.volume DESC\nLIMIT 30\n'''\n\ndf = pd.read_sql(query, conn)\nprint('Markets in volatile categories with decent volume/liquidity:')\nprint(df[['question', 'last_trade_price', 'volume', 'liquidity', 'market_category']].to_string())\nprint(f'\\\\nFound {len(df)} markets in volatile categories.')\nconn.close()\n\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":91,"output":447,"cacheRead":51648,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":52186,"cost":{"input":2.5480000000000002e-