ria normalize relations by December 31, 2026?             0.790  5.694852e+05   6280.35570\n34                                    Will John Ternus be the next CEO of Apple?             0.420  5.683315e+05   4113.09910\n35                           Will MetaMask launch a token by September 30, 2026?             0.800  5.671517e+05   4857.85900\n36                                          Will OpenAI be acquired before 2027?             0.098  5.651173e+05   3428.25391\n37       Will Delroy Lindo win Best Supporting Actor at the 98th Academy Awards?             0.056  5.640810e+05   6731.13485\n38                                    Will Base launch a token by June 30, 2026?             0.962  5.594747e+05   8144.92807\n39                                       Will Pizza Hut be acquired before 2027?             0.480  5.524744e+05   5210.05570\n\nFound 40 additional markets.","cwd":"/home/boldplane/.openclaw/agents/market-ranker"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773618561964}}
{"type":"message","id":"fe447b66","parentId":"97717442","timestamp":"2026-03-15T23:49:27.423Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! Now I have enough markets to create my 90-market list. Let me compile all the findings and create the final report. First, let me create the directory structure:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_hpsYXUKuOPKCa6XpWkMWx51s","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"mkdir -p ~/.openclaw/workspace/relevant_markets"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":1434,"output":92,"cacheRead":52864,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":54390,"cost":{"input":4.0152000000000003e-10,"output":3.8639999999999995e-11,"cacheRead":1.480192e-9,"cacheWrite":0,"total":1.920352e-9}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773618561972}}
