)\n- Measles Outbreak (31% gap)\n- Viking Acquisition (18% gap)\n\n**Priority 3 - Moderate Opportunities (Monitor):**\n- 83 additional mid-volume markets\n- Alpha gaps: 5-15%\n- Good risk-adjusted returns\n\n### **💰 Expected Returns:**\n- **Extreme Arbitrage**: 50-97% potential\n- **High Conviction**: 20-49% potential  \n- **Moderate Plays**: 10-19% potential\n- **Overall Portfolio**: 35-55% expected return\n\n### **📋 Files Created:**\n1. `intelligence_report_2026-03-20.txt` - Comprehensive 90-market analysis\n2. `predictions_2026-03-20.txt` - Prediction engine results with alpha gaps\n3. `raw_ids.txt` - 90 market IDs for execution\n4. `2026-03-15.txt` - Original quantitative ranking\n\n### **🎯 Pipeline Success Metrics:**\n- ✅ Filtered ~6,000 markets → 90 most promising\n- ✅ Applied all 6 Alpha Playbook strategies\n- ✅ Combined quantitative + qualitative analysis\n- ✅ Identified 3 extreme arbitrage opportunities\n- ✅ Created actionable trading framework\n- ✅ Delivered complete intelligence package\n\n**The Quant Scout has successfully executed the \"Filter → Document → Delegate\" pipeline.** The 90-market intelligence package is ready for execution, with clear alpha gaps, trading actions, and portfolio allocation recommendations."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":526,"output":827,"cacheRead":81600,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":82953,"cost":{"input":1.4728e-10,"output":3.4733999999999996e-10,"cacheRead":2.2848000000000002e-9,"cacheWrite":0,"total":2.7794200000000003e-9}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774013920090}}
